# Vue / Nuxt Engineering Rules

- Use `<script setup lang="ts">` and defineProps/defineEmits.
- Keep components small; use composables for logic.
- SSR-friendly APIs in Nuxt; guard client-only code.

## Performance
- Avoid reactive oversubscription; use `computed` and `watchEffect` wisely.
- Virtualize large lists.

## Security
- Escape dynamic HTML; server-validate params.

